;Mozilla Advocacy
Defensa de Mozilla


;Rallying citizens to protect the open Internet
Reunir le citatanos pro proteger internet aperte


;Mozilla’s advocacy engine works with allies to cultivate a global force of tens of millions of people, who are aware of the issues that are vital to the future of the open Internet and prepared to take action in support of the rights of citizens of the web.
Le motor de defensa Mozilla collabora con le alliatos pro cultivar un fortia global de decenas de milliones de personas, qui es conscie del problemas que es vital pro le futuro de internet aperte e preparate a prender action in supporto del derectos del citatanos del web.


;We are dedicated to building a world where:
Nos es dedicate a producer un mundo ubi:


;People are making more conscious choices to build and protect the open Internet
Le personas face electiones plus consciente pro construer e proteger internet aperte


;Companies and governments create products, policies and laws to support the open Internet because of public pressure to do so
Le companias e le governamentos crea productos, politicas e leges pro supportar internet aperte a causa del public pression pro lo facer


;How we work: A focus on depth and scale
Como nos labora: un foco sur profunditate e scala


;Mozilla’s advocacy approach incorporates both scale to depth and depth to scale to properly address the diversity of issues that we work on.
Le approche de defensa de Mozilla incorpora ambe le scala pro approfundar e le profunditate pro scalar pro adressar correctemente le diversitates de problemas que nos elabora.


;This approach enables Mozilla to simultaneously build our capacity to mobilize millions of people quickly and grow our organizing power in local communities, which will make it possible to win on our issues in the long-term.
Iste approche activa Mozilla a crear simultaneemente nostre capacitate pro mobilisar milliones de personas rapidemente e crescer nostre potentia de organisation in communitates local, que rendera possibile vincer sur nostre problemas in le longe-tempore.


;We also push ourselves to be proactive — setting the topic and tone of the conversation, and promoting solutions — as well as reactive to current events or undesirable policies when necessary.
Nos alsi pulsa nos mesmes a ser proactive — definir le topico e le tono del conversation, e promover solutiones — e tam ben reactive al actual eventos o politicas non desiderabile quando il necesse.


;Our initiatives
Nostre initiativas


;Mozilla’s Advocacy Engine consists of five key initiatives:
